%^BOLD%^-=%^RED%^Suffering Domain%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

Clerics who choose the suffering domain thrive upon inflicting pain on others, and sometimes even having it inflicted upon themselves. The domain grants access to spells that harness the very essence of agony itself, using it to damage and weaken opponents.

Clerics with the Suffering Domain gain the following Benefits:
- A +2 bonus spell DC versus Will Saves.
- %^RED%^BOLD%^Ray of Enfeeblement%^RESET%^ as an innate spell.

The suffering domain contains the following spells:

Wave of Pain, Boneshatter, Kiss of Torment, Caustic Eruption, Powerword Stun

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: The Faceless One, Khyron

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
